Native stag beetles
Native stag beetles were found for sale alongside exotic species during the market survey. Sales of at least eight native species or sub-species were confirmed (Table 4). Of these, Dorcus curvidens, D. titanus pilifer and D. titanus daitoensis are listed as Rare or Lower Risk in the Red Data Books of the Ministry of Environment and of several prefectures (see http://www. pref.okinawa.jp/okinawa_kankyo/rdb/code/rdb_1_wamei3.html).
